    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607382152488682070)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggE8Gr76nNy_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggE8Gr76nNy_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s1bximg.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gguIkD8Jj0g_text","label":"gguIkD8Jj0g_text","default":"<p>Women all over America are reporting that this 10-second trick is all they need to have smoother, firmer skin on their face, as well as a tighter, more youthful-looking neck.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcx0d-287Q_text","label":"ggcx0d-287Q_text","default":"<p>When the lip lines and mouth wrinkles won’t disappear, your jowls are softening and your neckline continues to droop and sag no matter what you try… There’s only one thing to blame: <strong>PROGERIN</strong>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrIT8j6Gse_text","label":"ggrIT8j6Gse_text","default":"<p>A nasty “aging protein” that destroys the healthy collagen and elastin fibers you need to have smooth, firm, lifted skin. While also preventing healthy new skin cells from bubbling to the surface so that you look younger and healthier.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggM83Xc3UVl_text","label":"ggM83Xc3UVl_text","default":"<p>To put it simply…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkfO2WC4nu_text","label":"ggkfO2WC4nu_text","default":"<p>Progerin keeps you stuck with skin you don’t like. It makes you look older, and will leave you wondering whether your skincare routine is really doing anything.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUpm_nIJW8_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggUpm_nIJW8_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s1img_6cc5cf3c-f383-4e86-bd1f-081ab2e53ebf.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAlgyIwsuu_text","label":"ggAlgyIwsuu_text","default":"<p>Yet while Progerin is bad news, there is something simple you can do to get it under control. Something that will stop Progerin from thinning and fraying your collagen and elastin so you can once again have beautifully firm, wrinkle-free skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwA8mnB55u_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggwA8mnB55u_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s1img_6cc5cf3c-f383-4e86-bd1f-081ab2e53ebf.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLJR58Kk8u_text","label":"ggLJR58Kk8u_text","default":"<p>A 10-second tweak to your morning routine that probably has more wrinkle-erasing and skin-tightening power than collagen and retinol combined.</p>"}],
